data.text: @valdes23 @RColesworthy @MTV You all too! Thanks for the trip down memory lane ✌🏾

@valdes23 @DominiqueJL15 @MTV Oh thank goodness! I'm going to have to go find clips of House of Style and the original true story of seven strangers picked to live in a loft so I'm well-prepared for our 90s trip down memory lane birthday celebration, Vanessa. Have a good night, you two!

@valdes23 @DominiqueJL15 @MTV I did just google and confirm that, as I thought, Daisy put in an appearance on a Bravo show a few years ago about interior decorators. She had a lovely home! (Because of course she did and, yes, I'll clearly watch anything.)
@valdes23 @DominiqueJL15 @MTV OH I REMEMBER THAT! No googling necessary! Which is why I'm so shocked that I missed their marriage.
@DominiqueJL15 @valdes23 @MTV WAIT how did I not know that she has been married to Richard Marx since 2015?! WHAT?! I can't believe I didn't know this.

@valdes23 @RColesworthy @MTV And STAYS hustling! Can’t walk into a Kohl’s or Burlington’s without seeing her stuff. Wouldn’t be surprised if she lowkey pulled a Jessica Simpson and built herself a cute lil billion dollar empire out here.
@valdes23 @DominiqueJL15 @MTV Admittedly I also love Norman because of course I do

@valdes23 @DominiqueJL15 @MTV I love Heather B and Kevin Powell has been major. Also now I can picture Julie in her dance class b/c she was...a dancer weirdly?! AND whenever I have family visiting I think of Julie when her parents visited NYC saying "the plan is to wear them out." IT WAS 25 YRS AGO WHO AM I?

@valdes23 @DominiqueJL15 @MTV DAISY FUENTES!!! Now you are talking! Please tell me that we get to talk about SEASON 1 of The Real World after this. Also, I am now remembering that when I went to South Beach in high school I was so excited that there was a Todd Oldham store that I bought some random necklace.
@valdes23 @RColesworthy @MTV Daisy! She was so so fly, there are Instagram girls probably wearing this outfit RIGHT NOW. https://t.co/AM6xMGIQJp

@valdes23 @DominiqueJL15 @MTV Oh you mean THIS Dan Cortese tweet, which was liked BY Dan Cortese? (Took me a while to dig that out of the notifications--but it's him!) You will not be surprised to hear that my mother takes GREAT pride in my having been raised on MTV and I of course LOVED House of Style. https://t.co/lyQInTCYCD

@valdes23 @MTV @RColesworthy Hahaha my love for Kevyn Aucoin stretches the highest limits of my heart, and my font. He’s so important to me. Literally just took down his books from my shelf to have a flick through ❤️
@valdes23 @MTV HE MADE THE ULTIMA II NAKEDS COLLECTION!!! Urban Decay/these Kardashians are out here lying to the children like they invented the nude palette.

@valdes23 @MTV WHO DOESN’T REMEMBER KEVYN AUCOIN?!?!

Was just reminiscing about how his books were my first exposure to LGBTQ history/culture. He wrote about his parents joining PFLAG, and his makeup look with a trans friend was the first time I ever heard of trans issues and identity.
